kgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實文青打扮都好講究飾物，冷帽，漁夫帽同畫家帽都比較常見<br />\n個啲哈利波特眼鏡就算9數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中長襪加oxford shoes就當然必備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以既話加返隻皮錶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 袋既就皮既袋同帆布袋都可以"},{"pid":"4df8ac84ab0b523f87249bf2283abcab266a8718","tid":33224,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T19:28:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddaabec6de7a3fddf9af12da68188183667c3bee","tid":33224,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T10:06:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88f1a1758d905eb57ee2008b266536b32edfed9e","tid":33224,"uid":43678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T10:13:30.000Z","msg":"咩身型先得架"},{"pid":"3d710aa9212074f70d4b1d20c295655aa4b74636","tid":33224,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T10:19:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩身型先得架</blockquote><br />\n同第三張相差唔多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n162，唔知幾多磅"},{"pid":"c024dbce6b2caed6ae8af5d106cb3e29e70bd345","tid":33224,"uid":16408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:02:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E36D51E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE36D51E.jpg&h=617f0448&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢套幾好 文青得黎又有啲型格感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}